{"tid":1383914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲撕連儂牆其實唔係壞事 可以更新最新文宣","createTime":"2019-07-29T19:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:53:09.000Z","uid":138609,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a4cea2ba419cc02f6518c2bf9e2db0bf941c75ad","tid":1383914,"uid":138609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T19:58:13.000Z","msg":"連儂牆係社區最重要既文宣平台<br />\n觀察下就知好多中老年人 師奶會睇<br />\n佢地通常資訊接觸單一 易被媒體導向<br />\n民建聯社區工作既重點對象就係佢地<br />\n藍絲咪好鐘意撕連儂牆<br />\n但香港人重建連儂牆速度同決心係堅決既<br />\n正好藉此換返上新既文宣<br />\n過期文宣有人幫手拆仲好添<br />\n班藍絲建制狗係班低智商生物<br />\n兼淨係識收錢做野<br />\n講速度創意我地一定贏梗<br />\n所以唔洗因為佢地撕而嬲<br />\n反而係班藍絲自掘墳墓"},{"pid":"f9c46f49a9e10ce3ac672b431b6be1a06fc09251","tid":1383914,"uid":138609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T20:07:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a16d0e19d00ec3f5df6aeca5f8ef8757ad41800","tid":1383914,"uid":55936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T22:16:38.000Z","msg":"撕咪由佢囉，反正要搵位update吓！"},{"pid":"ada2aa3eb31b418f083bba9b385264ca3db75667","tid":1383914,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"用鎖頭！<br />\n<br />\nE.g. 喺尖東海傍建立一個「連儂海傍」景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等大陸人打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ApM28As.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FApM28As.png&h=00b9d1fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/APRFVfu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAPRFVfu.png&h=6c611bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkyXYkA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkyXYkA.png&h=7dfc92f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[永久連儂牆］點解唔用鎖頭？<br />\n